
Beckett Hall, the namesake of Beckett Hall Circle, is a former Residence Halls dorm located on campus at UC Davis. It was built in 1951. A mens dorm, in 1964 on February 1st, KDVS started broadcasting from the original studio located in the laundry room.  They used the dorms  wiki:wikipedia:Carrier current electrical wiring to transmit, so Beckett Hall was also the original KDVS transmitter.
